s="gf_gs_ct">Mindful Meditation</h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1660936504622" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1660936504622"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>So how do you apply or use mindfulness?&nbsp;</p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.025em; text-align: inherit;">Below is a helpful step by step description of how to use mindful meditation,&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.025em; text-align: inherit;">with information from an article by Harvard staff writer Liz Mineo.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.025em; text-align: inherit;">Mindful Meditation Made Easy¹³</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1660936798921" class="gf_row gf_gs-spacing-xl-m-top gf_row-gap-20" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1660936798921" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="20px" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1660936798945" data-id="1660936798945"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1660936831123" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1660936831123" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/4e6522f5-3855-41ac-a6ea-bb9d16c4ff57/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Frame%2067.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="302" height="302" data-width="10%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="302" natural-height="302"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1660936981199" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1660936981199"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs_ct">Settle in</h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1660936940375" class="element-wrap gf_gs-spacing-lg-m-top" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1660936940375"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs_ct gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Find a quiet space. Using a cushion or chair, sit up straight but not stiff; allow your head and shoulders to rest comfortably; place your hands on the tops of your legs with upper arms at&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.025em; text-align: inherit;">your side.</span></p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1660937554079" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-20 gf_gs-spacing-xl-m-top" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1660937554079" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="20px" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1660936798945" data-id="1660936798945"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1660937554059" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1660937554059" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/4e6522f5-3855-41ac-a6ea-bb9d16c4ff57/-/forma