 excessive alcohol / tobacco, and continue with routine preventative measures by consulting with your primary health care provider.¹<span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px; font-size: 9.6px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat; text-align: left;">5</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat; text-align: left;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.025em; text-align: inherit;">&nbsp;</span></p></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" id="e-1660940354448" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1660940354448"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1660940354397" class="element-wrap gf_gs-spacing-md-m-top gf_gs-spacing-md-m-left" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1660940354397"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs_ct gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-center" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="text-align: inherit!important;"><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; font-family: Montserrat;">¹⁴</span><span style="text-align: inherit; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; font-family: Montserrat;">https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2018/04/less-stress-clearer-thoughts-with-mindfulness-meditation/</span></p><p style="text-align: inherit!important;"><font face="Montserrat"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px;">¹⁵ &nbsp;https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/daily-life-coping/managing-stress-anxiety.ht