ies, essential workers and unpaid adult caregivers have experienced disproportionately worse mental health outcomes. The mental health conditions reported by U.S. adults are shown in the infographic below.²</p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1661267663416" class="element-wrap gf_gs-spacing-md-m-top" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1661267663416"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs_ct gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font face="Montserrat"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px;">¹ https://www.who.int/disabilities/world_report/2011/chapter3.pdf</span></font></p><p><font face="Montserrat"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px;">² https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/69/wr/mm6932a1.htm</span></font></p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1661267328852" class="gf_row gf_row-fluid gf_row-no-padding gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1661267328852" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="0px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1661267328886" data-id="1661267328886"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1661267340045" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1661267340045" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/92d0ba65-ecbc-4ff3-b648-df0cb6132a43/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Untitled-1.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1280" height="3000" natural-width="1280" natural-height="3000"></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1661267558331" class="gf_row gf_gs-spacing-lg-m-top gf_gs-spacing-lg-m-bottom gf_row-gap-20 gf_row-fluid gf_row-no-paddi