div></div></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-md-9 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-sm-9" id="c-1614760295764" data-id="1614760295764"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1661267558298" class="element-wrap gf_gs-spacing-sm-m-top" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1661267558298"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-justify-lg gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf_gs-spacing-md-p-left" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: justify;">Meditation is a broad term that includes the practice of achieving definitive consciousness and concentration. Meditation can include several modalities or techniques to accomplish this enhanced level of consciousness including compassion, love, patience, and mindfulness, which is a type of meditation.</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px; font-size: 9.6px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat;">3</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.025em;">Mindful Meditation is about focusing on the present one breath at a time. It also includes mindful sitting meditation, mindful eating, appreciation meditation, friendly or loving-kindness meditation, mindful walking, and mindful movement otherwise known as mindful awareness practices (MAPS)</span><font color="#1c1d1d" face="Montserrat" style="font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.025em;">.</font><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px; font-size: 9.6px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat;">4&nbsp;</span><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1661267558426" class="element-wrap gf_gs-spacing-md-m-top gf_gs-spacing-md-m-right" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1661267558426"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs_ct gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left gf_gs-spacing-md-p-left" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="font-family: Roboto; font-size: 10px; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(134, 134, 134);"><font face="Montserrat"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px;">³ https://www.medicaldaily.com/mindfulness-meditation-differences-377346</span></font></p><p style="font-family: Roboto; font-size: 10px; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(134, 134, 134);"><font face="Montserrat"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px;">⁴ https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/balanced/201907/meditation-and-mental-health#:</span></font></p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1661269128088" class="gf_row gf_row-fluid gf_row-no-padding" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1661269128088" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1661269128096" data-id="1661269128096"><div data-label="Carousel" data-key="carousel" data-atomgroup="module" id="m-1661269147079" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-carousel" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1661269147079"><div class="module main-slider owl-carousel owl-theme " data-collg="3" data-colmd="3" data-colsm="1" data-colxs="1" data-marginlg="5px" data-marginmd="5px" data-marginsm="5px" data-marginxs="5px" data-dotslg="1" data-dotsmd="1" data-dotssm="1" data-dotsxs="1" data-navlg="1" data-navmd="1" data-navsm="0" data-navxs="0" data-navspeed="1000" data-autoplay="1" data-autoplaytimeout="3500" data-autoplayhoverpause="1" data-loop="1"><div class="item"><div data-index="1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1661269162578" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1661269162578" data-resolution="